title: Harems Price Drop Proposal
body: All current members will be allowed to mint as many harems as possible for .001 of a penny. We will drop the price and let others join; Harems collection will cap this number. Once the collection hits this number, Harems Smart Contract will turn off the sale function.
author: 0x37f0945Dc06BF627d4cF875Be442b012eCCd53cb
